save

void save(com.ibm.team.workitem.common.internal.enumeration.Enumeration enumeration,
          org.eclipse.core.runtime.IProgressMonitor monitor)
          throws TeamRepositoryException
Stores the given enumeration into the database updating any existing enumeration if provided. This method will throw a PermissionDeniedException if the authenticated user is missing permissions to modify the process specification of the project area this enumeration is associated with.

Parameters:
enumeration - the enumeration to save.
Throws:
TeamRepositoryException - in case of an error.
PermissionDeniedException - in case the user performing this operation has no rights to modify the project area specification.

delete

void delete(com.ibm.team.workitem.common.internal.enumeration.EnumerationHandle enumeration,
            org.eclipse.core.runtime.IProgressMonitor monitor)
            throws TeamRepositoryException
Deletes a persisted enumeration from the database. This method will throw a PermissionDeniedException if the authenticated user is missing permissions to modify the process specification of the project area this enumeration is associated with.

Parameters:
enumeration - the persisted enumeration to delete.
Throws:
TeamRepositoryException - in case of an error.
PermissionDeniedException - in case the user performing this operation has no rights to modify the project area specification.
